      "notes": [
        {
          "category": "summary",
          "text": "Sending a specially crafted packet to Port 102/TCP of an affected device could cause a denial-of-service condition. A restart is needed to restore normal operations.CVE-2021-33737 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 7.5 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H).",
